# iCloud (bajia@me.com)
IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
Port 993
User bajia@me.com
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -a bajia@me.com -s imap.mail.me.com -w"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mails/iCloud/
Inbox ~/Mails/iCloud/INBOX

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns INBOX Drafts Sent Junk Trash
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 200
ExpireUnread yes


# Gmail (daichao@gmail.com)
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User daichao@gmail.com
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -a daichao@gmail.com -s imap.gmail.com -w"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mails/Gmail/
Inbox ~/Mails/Gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX "Sent Messages" "Deleted Messages" Drafts "[Gmail]/Spam"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 200
ExpireUnread yes
